%% Diagram: Getting Started Flow
%% Type: flowchart
flowchart LR
    install[Install<br/>npm add diagramkit] --> warmup[Warmup<br/>npx diagramkit warmup]
    warmup --> create[Create Diagram<br/>.mermaid .excalidraw<br/>.drawio .dot]
    create --> render[Render<br/>npx diagramkit render]
    render --> output[".diagramkit/<br/>diagram-light.svg<br/>diagram-dark.svg"]
